Dr Christopher Valentine was sacked from a sexual health clinic nine years ago for taking illicit photos of patients . 
  He was not struck off and went on to work at an NHS service for drug addicts and alcoholics . 
  A nurse saw images of a semi-naked man on his iPod Touch on a night out . 
  Tribunal heard he used his iPod to take 53 photos of vulnerable patients . 
